                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Written in a mediocre handwriting.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                        <date notBefore="1400" notAfter="1499">15th century</date>
                        <desc>
                           Some paleographic features: 
                           ሎ has the loop marking the 7th order attached directly to the body of the letter, without the linking line; 
                           the bodies of some letters, e.g. የ, ደ, ጸ, and the upper loop of ቆ and ቶ, have a triangular shape; 
                           numerals are written without dashes; 
                           the crux ansata is seldom used in the right margin in correspondence of the beginning of the psalms.
                        </desc>
                        <seg type="rubrication">
                           Nomina sacra; numbers and titles of the psalms and the canticles; the crux ansata.
                        </seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>The shelfmark <q xml:lang="la">Vat. | 7 | Aethiop.</q> is written on the cover, together with the coat of arms of pope <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7893PiusIX">Pius IX</persName>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc>Subsections of the psalms are indicated by means of several signs, e .g., ፲ (<locus target="#1v"/>,  <locus target="#46v"/>, etc.), 
                              ፲፪ (<locus target="#27v"/>), ፻፪(<locus from="34" to="38"/>), and circles with ሀ, ወ, ዐ, የ.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>Crosses and other signs are inserted with no apparent purpose, e.g., on <locus target="#10"/>, <locus target="#37v"/>,
                              <locus target="#42v"/>, <locus target="#58"/>, <locus target="#72"/>, <locus target="#78"/>, <locus target="#80v"/>, 
                              <locus target="#99"/>, <locus target="#99v"/>, <locus target="#103"/>, <locus target="#107"/>, <locus target="#118"/>, 
                              <locus target="#119"/>, <locus target="#120"/>, <locus target="#123v"/>, <locus target="#129"/>.
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4">
                           <desc>Five lines are left unfilled on <locus target="#133rb"/> after the words <q xml:lang="gez">ወመሥዋዕተ፡ ክቡረ፡</q>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e5">
                           <desc>Doodles at the bottom of <locus target="#133vb"/>.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
            
